\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">5</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">6</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.5</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>Now, for the strategy where we can roll a second time, the optimal strategy is to roll again when the first roll is below the expected value (i.e., 1, 2, or 3) because on average, the second roll should be higher.</p>\n<p>So, if we roll a 1, 2, or 3, we should roll again, and the expected value of that roll is again 3.5. If we roll a 4, 5, or 6, we should keep it.</p>\n<p>Therefore, the expected value of the game under this optimal strategy is:</p>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>3.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>3.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>3.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>6</mn></mfrac></mstyle><mo>⋅</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 3.5 + \\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 3.5 + \\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 3.5 + \\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 4 + \\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 5 + \\dfrac{1}{6} \\cdot 6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0074em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3214em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">6</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3.5</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;